files.patch:
@@ -63,19 +63,0 @@
-AGENT_PREFIX := lib
-AGENT_EXT := .so
-
-# Setup _NT_SYMBOL_PATH on Windows, which points to our pdb files.
-ifeq ($(call isTargetOs, windows), true)
-  AGENT_PREFIX :=
-  AGENT_EXT := .dll
-  ifndef _NT_SYMBOL_PATH
-    SYMBOL_PATH := $(call PathList, $(sort $(patsubst %/, %, $(dir $(wildcard \
-        $(addprefix $(SYMBOLS_IMAGE_DIR)/bin/, *.pdb */*.pdb))))))
-    export _NT_SYMBOL_PATH := $(subst \\,\, $(call FixPath, \
-        $(subst $(DQUOTE),, $(SYMBOL_PATH))))
-    $(call LogDebug, Setting _NT_SYMBOL_PATH to $(_NT_SYMBOL_PATH))
-  endif
-endif
-
-ifeq ($(call isTargetOs, macosx), true)
-    AGENT_EXT := .dyLib
-endif
@@ -215,2 +196,3 @@
-        TEST_MODE ASSERT VERBOSE RETAIN TEST_THREAD_FACTORY JVMTI_STRESS_AGENT MAX_MEM RUN_PROBLEM_LISTS \
-        RETRY_COUNT REPEAT_COUNT MAX_OUTPUT REPORT AOT_JDK $(CUSTOM_JTREG_SINGLE_KEYWORDS), \
+        TEST_MODE ASSERT VERBOSE RETAIN TEST_THREAD_FACTORY JVMTI_STRESS_AGENT \
+        MAX_MEM RUN_PROBLEM_LISTS RETRY_COUNT REPEAT_COUNT MAX_OUTPUT REPORT \
+        AOT_JDK $(CUSTOM_JTREG_SINGLE_KEYWORDS), \
@@ -888,1 +870,1 @@
-    AGENT := $${AGENT_PREFIX}JvmtiStressAgent${AGENT_EXT}=$${JTREG_JVMTI_STRESS_AGENT}
+    AGENT := $${LIBRARY_PREFIX}JvmtiStressAgent${SHARED_LIBRARY_SUFFIX}=$${JTREG_JVMTI_STRESS_AGENT}
